title: Close-up with the Acer Predator gaming line
description:
For more on Acer's Predator products, check out: http://unlocked.newegg.com/review-acer-predator-15-gaming-laptop/

In this interview from Newegg's We Own the Night 2015 BlizzCon after-party, Eric Ackerson from Acer takes us through the company's new Predator line of gaming hardware.

For more gaming news, visit http://GameCrate.com

Intro music by Random aka Mega Ran (http://megaran.com)
